                  ; one pair of breeches, value 10 s., and one waistcoat, value 5 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18190421-6-victim134" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Fitch
                  <interp inst="t18190421-6-victim134" type="surname" value="Fitch"></interp>
